Class SqlMetaText

java.lang.Object
org.sqlproc.engine.impl.SqlMetaText
All Implemented Interfaces:
SqlMetaElement, SqlMetaSimple
class SqlMetaText extends Object implements SqlMetaSimple
A META SQL sub-element. It represents a text without any semantic value for a META SQL generation.
Author:
Vladimir Hudec
